description: Kansas' premier Hawaiian food truck is rolling down a streets near you! Noble House Hawaiian Plate Lunch is bringing you the best in authentic Hawaiian cuisine. Delicious Kalua pig, Kalbi ribs, poke, katsu, and so much more are coming right to you! Noble House Hawaiian Plate Lunch is a food truck you're sure to love, so be on the lookout for it today!
name: Noble House Hawaiian Plate Lunch
